des: Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. I have created this game for first time using template ,you all will know about Guru Granth Sahib Ji facts while playing this game..there are sort of questions which u have to choose the correct answer and just like the formal quiz we play...i hope u all will like this game...please tried it once....it will also gave me opportunity to learn more and share with you as well ...
